## *k*-means clustering

::: {.fragment}
1\. Start with *k* randomly chosen means
:::

::: {.fragment}
2\. Color data points by the shortest distance to any
mean
:::

::: {.fragment}
3\. Move means to centroid position of each group of
points
:::

::: {.fragment}
4\. Repeat from step 2 until convergence
:::

